 Two features of netrek that I just learned this last week, after months
 playing the game:

 (1) If you detonate the enemy's torps, they won't hurt your teammates at all.
 Useful to know when you're escorting a planet-taker.  The explosions
 will hurt you, of course. They also seem to hurt your enemies (other than
 the guy who fired them?).

