 Note that these weapon temps are in tenths, relative to what you see on
 the client's display.

 Other things that might be interesting to figure out include:
         Fuel used at max warp, per second, including what you recharge.
         Total amount of damage you can possibly do with one tank of fuel.
         Time to get from one home world to another without overheating, and
         how much fuel you'd have left.
